text: Nichi is a given name and nickname, and may refer to: * Nichi Farnham (born 1963), American politician * Nichi Hodgson (born 1983), British journalist, broadcaster, and author * Nichi Vendola (born 1958), Italian politician ==See also== * Nicci (disambiguation) * Nicki, a given name Category:Nicknames Category:Feminine given names
